Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.74,0:00:03.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm having a birthday.\NI want you to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.03,0:00:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.66,0:00:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of easy to talk to you\Nthese days, Fujinuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.33,0:00:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.46,0:00:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's because\NI decided not to lie to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.96,0:00:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I just said that out loud.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.34,0:00:20.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hinazuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.97,0:00:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.80,0:00:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is the last place\NI saw Hinazuki 18 years ago.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.98,0:00:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Her body was found\Nafter the snow melted...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.81,0:00:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but what day did she disappear in March?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.81,0:00:36.06,Crash,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GIRL
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.06,0:00:36.31,Crash,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ISOLATION
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.31,0:00:36.56,Crash,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DISAPPEARANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.56,0:00:36.82,Crash,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ABDUCT
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.82,0:00:37.27,Crash,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DEAD
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.36,0:00:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I can figure that out,\NI can prevent it from happening.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.61,0:00:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}NIPPON\NSHOWA'S MOST SHOCKING CRIMES
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.28,0:00:51.33,Sign Left,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AYA NAKANISHI\N(11 YEARS OLD)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.28,0:00:51.33,Sign Right,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KAYO HINAZUKI\N(10 YEARS OLD)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.28,0:00:51.33,SignNC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HIROMI SUGITA\N(11 YEARS OLD)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.03,0:00:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Aya Nakanishi...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.16,0:00:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hiromi Sugita...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.00,0:00:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hiromi Souda, too...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.33,0:00:53.96,SignNC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KAYO HINAZUKI\N(10 YEARS OLD)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.83,0:00:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But only Hinazuki was ten years old.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.50,0:00:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In other words, when Hinazuki\Nwent missing in March,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.67,0:00:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}she hadn't had her birthday yet.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.38,0:01:06.97,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MARCH
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.75,0:01:05.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}X-day is between March 1st\Nand Hinazuki's birthday.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.93,0:02:33.22,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ERASED
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.02,0:02:39.48,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Hockey Club\N1988 National Champions
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.23,0:02:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.82,0:02:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hear the boys are gonna\Nrace each other one on one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.53,0:02:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.32,0:02:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This should be fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.57,0:02:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm sure Hamada's gonna\Nget the best time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.66,0:02:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.20,0:02:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hamada!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.50,0:02:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}- Ice hockey team!\N- Hamada, do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.79,0:02:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}- Good luck!\N- Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.50,0:02:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, already.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.04,0:03:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.05,0:03:06.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna hold back, y'know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.84,0:03:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.09,0:03:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hamada is a regular\Non the ice hockey team,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.18,0:03:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the kind who'd win\Nthe national championship.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.39,0:03:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come to think of it,\NI remember racing against him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.85,0:03:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fujinuma is racing Hamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.94,0:03:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Poor guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.40,0:03:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hinazuki, you should cheer him on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.32,0:03:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Hinazuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.03,0:03:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fujinuma, are you going to win?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.53,0:03:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go as fast as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.12,0:03:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Then good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.37,0:03:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,On your mark...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.33,0:03:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Get set...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.21,0:03:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.30,0:03:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- All right! Go!\N- Satoru, go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.47,0:03:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.34,0:03:54.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Hamada, what are you doing?!\N- Try harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.31,0:03:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This guy is fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.97,0:03:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fujinuma probably started\Nbefore the pistol went off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.48,0:04:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is it okay to win?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.19,0:04:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Would victory have any meaning?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.44,0:04:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.94,0:04:11.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This guy goes through\Nhard training every day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.66,0:04:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The winner should be...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.46,0:04:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.12,0:04:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I knew Hamada would win in the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.42,0:04:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.71,0:04:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He gave Hamada a run for his money!\NThat's a big deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.72,0:04:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Kenya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.10,0:04:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fujinuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.22,0:04:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hate punks like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.40,0:04:46.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.07,0:04:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was a close one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.11,0:04:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.11,0:04:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with Hamada?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.99,0:04:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know. Just because he almost lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.41,0:04:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.99,0:04:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I remember.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.70,0:05:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I hate punks like you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.50,0:05:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I made the same mistake\NI did 18 years ago.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.80,0:05:17.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Hinazuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.47,0:05:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hamada really was fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.85,0:05:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.06,0:05:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.85,0:05:27.06,BigSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,X-DAY
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.27,0:05:27.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,tell me your birthday, Hinazuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.11,0:05:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.57,0:05:37.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You said you wouldn't lie to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.99,0:05:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.04,0:05:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason, I thought\NHamada should win today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.16,0:05:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.54,0:05:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.25,0:05:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.50,0:05:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're both fakes and liars.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.80,0:06:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru, wanna walk home together?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.35,0:06:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! I left something\Nin the room, so go on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.19,0:06:10.07,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}STAFF ROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.49,0:06:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}5th Grade, Class 4\NHomeroom Teacher\NGaku Yashiro
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.88,0:06:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Satoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.42,0:06:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yashiro-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.42,0:06:34.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.55,0:06:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is it about Kayo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.09,0:06:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His intuition is good...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.34,0:06:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to look up\Nher birthday. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.39,0:06:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.10,0:06:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru, it seems like\Nyou've gotten friendly with Kayo lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.48,0:06:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.27,0:06:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't ask her directly?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.23,0:06:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I told her my birthday,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.98,0:06:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but she wouldn't tell me hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.15,0:06:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.45,0:06:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here, see for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.99,0:07:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What do you mean, "that makes sense?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.78,0:07:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kayo Hinazuki - March 2nd\NSatoru Fujinuma - March 2nd
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.37,0:07:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The same day as me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.83,0:07:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.75,0:07:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.91,0:07:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Kayo is pretty shy, so it was probably hard\Nfor her to say that you share the same birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.00,0:07:15.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably a good idea to celebrate it\Nwith her without thinking too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.84,0:07:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.51,0:07:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well... excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.59,0:07:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.97,0:07:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was a close race today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.02,0:07:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Doing your best\Nis the key to everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.73,0:07:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you with Kayo, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.77,0:07:29.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.48,0:07:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gaku Yashiro...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.19,0:07:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's about my age in this time period.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.57,0:07:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And he's got a sharp, observing eye.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.87,0:07:46.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know when X-day is.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.33,0:07:50.83,BigSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MARCH 1st
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.79,0:07:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}March 1st.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.83,0:07:57.09,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}February 19th{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.25,0:07:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}11 days from now...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.21,0:07:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}First, I have to make up with Hinazuki.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.09,0:08:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? She's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.69,0:08:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.32,0:08:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yuuki!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.82,0:08:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-It looks like\Nyou've made lots of friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.08,0:08:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.33,0:08:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yuuki is 23 years old in this time period.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.25,0:08:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's younger than me now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.75,0:08:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's thanks to you, Yuuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.34,0:08:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, it isn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.75,0:08:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-It's because\Nyou mustered up courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.13,0:08:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The feeling you had of wanting to have fun\Nwith everyone g-got across.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.97,0:08:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His stuttering and softhearted soul\Nare just like I remember.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.97,0:08:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's a good person.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.23,0:08:53.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuki, do you know Kayo Hinazuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.06,0:08:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo? Sure I know her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.65,0:08:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That was a quick answer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.07,0:09:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's always in the park alone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.99,0:09:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've talked to her a number of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.24,0:09:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is she a classmate?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.20,0:09:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.95,0:09:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh. I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.99,0:09:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jun! Time to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.00,0:09:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can start without me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.29,0:09:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it early for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.00,0:09:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We get up early.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.79,0:09:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I work at my dad's bento shop\Nfrom four in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.80,0:09:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Four?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.72,0:09:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. But just until noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.05,0:09:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.34,0:09:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We always hung out in the afternoon,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.30,0:09:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so I assumed he was unemployed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.60,0:09:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now that I'm 29,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.52,0:09:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can tell he's making an effort\Nto curb his dialect when he talks to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.31,0:09:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To a kid, the way he talks\Nhas a persuasiveness and maturity.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.11,0:09:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tell me about the way he talked.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.82,0:09:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did you think he was a good person?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.41,0:09:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There was another feature\Non the papercrafting tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.75,0:09:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um... Someone gave them to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.71,0:09:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,a-a-and I couldn't just throw them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.84,0:10:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.96,0:10:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Was there anything in his room\Nthat made you feel uneasy?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.26,0:10:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd better get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.81,0:10:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.94,0:10:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru, you've become\Nmore mature somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.07,0:10:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.74,0:10:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.62,0:10:36.33,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JUN SHIRATORI
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.62,0:10:36.33,LowSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MAY 2006, DEATH ROW PRISONER
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.70,0:10:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jun Shiratori.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.08,0:10:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In my present of 2006,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.99,0:10:33.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}he's a prisoner on Death Row.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.62,0:10:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ever since the first trial,\Nhe's claimed to be innocent.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.42,0:10:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I just can't believe\Nthat Yuuki would kill anyone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.38,0:10:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If the abductions don't take place,\Nhe won't be a suspect or anything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.68,0:10:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yuuki, wait for me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.43,0:10:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I promise to...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.64,0:10:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's not home yet?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.40,0:11:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's kind of a dump.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.03,0:11:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.49,0:11:12.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gloves!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.45,0:11:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't tell me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.84,0:11:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hinazuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.59,0:11:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.22,0:11:31.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Close it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.10,0:11:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,N-No. You'll catch cold in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.31,0:11:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.98,0:11:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's wrong, Kayo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.65,0:11:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're in here alone again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.94,0:11:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.65,0:11:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She did this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.12,0:11:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Get in the house right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.46,0:12:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.55,0:12:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How did Hinazuki get hurt like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.59,0:12:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Answer him, Kayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.23,0:12:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.86,0:12:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I couldn't find the words\Nto answer Hinazuki's sad lie.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.78,0:12:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And she wouldn't look at me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.04,0:12:43.96,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Episode 3\NBirthmark
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.51,0:12:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Kayo. Cool down!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.72,0:12:57.60,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ICE
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.72,0:13:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You need to get that face\Nhealed by Monday!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.35,0:13:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, everyone will blame me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.69,0:13:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.07,0:13:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Leave some ice for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.91,0:13:22.62,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}February 22nd{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.00,0:13:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's not here...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.76,0:13:35.47,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}On Duty:\NKayo Hinazuki, Satoru Fujinuma{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.80,0:13:37.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Satoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.18,0:13:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.51,0:13:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.97,0:13:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, it's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.14,0:13:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To find the radius,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.85,0:13:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you multiply the diameter by 3.14,\Nwhich is the circumference.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.98,0:13:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And if you do the opposite,\Nyou'll get the diameter,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.19,0:13:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so if you split that in half—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.57,0:13:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hinazuki...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.70,0:13:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. Take your seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.33,0:14:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, who will solve this at the board?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.12,0:14:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How about Satou? Will you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.75,0:14:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.04,0:14:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on. It's easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.47,0:14:16.43,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SCHOOL LUNCH FEE
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.43,0:14:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}School Lunch Fee{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.72,0:14:18.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're collecting the school lunch fee!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.14,0:14:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to change...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.60,0:14:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Please put it in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.22,0:14:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...the future.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.68,0:14:25.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you forgot today, bring it tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.69,0:14:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The reason Kayo is often late\Nor absent on Mondays...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.23,0:14:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know, Satoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.15,0:14:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because Hinazuki's mother\Nbeats her on Saturday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.32,0:14:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Then you've noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.16,0:14:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You knew, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.74,0:14:43.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.08,0:14:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? Sensei, tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.41,0:14:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've been struggling with the idea\Nof talking to the students about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.17,0:14:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even in class, Kayo is cut off\Nfrom everyone else, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.67,0:14:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought if everyone knew\Nshe was being physically abused,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.34,0:14:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,they would be prejudiced against her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.43,0:14:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.55,0:15:00.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know, Satoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.85,0:15:01.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For you, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.89,0:15:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'll tell you everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.43,0:15:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But don't share it with your classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.35,0:15:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.98,0:15:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I began to suspect\NKayo's mother last May.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.07,0:15:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But there weren't any tangible signs yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.28,0:15:17.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.53,0:15:20.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo's mother craftily hid the marks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.99,0:15:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Child Consultation Center\Nvisited their house three times,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.04,0:15:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but maybe the mother\Nhas good intuition
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.50,0:15:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,because each time she and Kayo\Nwere out of the house,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.67,0:15:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so an official interview\Nhasn't been conducted yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.33,0:15:33.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?\NThen they're incompetent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.88,0:15:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I said that out loud.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.21,0:15:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.05,0:15:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen the mother a number of times,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.43,0:15:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and physical abuse is definitely going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.05,0:15:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now the Child Consultation Center\Njust has to confirm it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.97,0:15:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then they'll take Kayo away\Nfrom her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.81,0:15:50.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So he's already made\Nthe preliminary arrangements.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.60,0:15:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But once that happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.82,0:15:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo won't be in class anymore, Satoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.99,0:15:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If it saves Hinazuki, I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.95,0:16:01.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.74,0:16:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm positive Yashiro is waiting\Nuntil spring vacation before taking action.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.12,0:16:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But it'll be too late by then!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.17,0:16:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hurry, dammit!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.54,0:16:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sit down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.96,0:16:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}D-Dammit...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.26,0:16:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's gone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.26,0:16:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The lunch money is gone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.43,0:16:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}29 years old and I've gotta\Nbe involved in an incident like this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.68,0:16:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.06,0:16:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.35,0:16:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's lunch money
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.19,0:16:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.23,0:16:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me! Not gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.23,0:16:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think somebody must have stolen it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.57,0:16:41.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm suspicious of Hinazuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.99,0:16:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... On what grounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.16,0:16:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all, Hinazuki\Ndoesn't pay for her lunches,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.50,0:16:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and I think the culprit has to be\Nsomebody who's poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.62,0:16:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That may be right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.71,0:16:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you take it, Hinazuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.88,0:16:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Little brat...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.13,0:17:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think the truth will come out\Nif we do a search of everyone's bags.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.97,0:17:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I agree!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.13,0:17:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Jeez. I just wanna eat lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.18,0:17:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to look?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.60,0:17:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't take it,\Nso what's the point of lookin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.56,0:17:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Search the bag of the person next to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.02,0:17:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you stole it, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.48,0:17:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.36,0:17:17.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, find the thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.23,0:17:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't find anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.36,0:17:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then it was Hinazuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.65,0:17:20.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.65,0:17:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Poor! Poor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.61,0:17:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.70,0:17:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- It was Hinazuki!\N- The poor girl really did do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.87,0:17:28.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See? Just like I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.79,0:17:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo is the thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.87,0:17:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.12,0:17:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if she's poor or hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.08,0:17:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hinazuki would never\Nsteal from anybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.42,0:17:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You probably did it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.38,0:17:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, anyone could've taken it\Nfrom Satoru's desk and planted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.52,0:17:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! Kayo is on duty today,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.94,0:17:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so there's nothing unusual\Nabout her having the lunch money.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.40,0:17:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Misato, Satoru,\Nthat's the end of it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.90,0:18:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.53,0:18:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.32,0:18:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.70,0:18:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}School is out, everyone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.87,0:18:11.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Students who are still in the building,\Nplease turn off the lights...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.74,0:18:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is awkward.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.58,0:18:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fujinuma, thanks for before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.37,0:18:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. What she said\Nwas totally uncalled-for.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.67,0:18:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In third grade,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.38,0:18:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Misato kept making fun of my pencils,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.84,0:18:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so I threw her prized\Nmechanical pencil out the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.80,0:18:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's hated me ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.64,0:18:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Although it's mutual...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.93,0:18:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But she once invited me\Nto a Christmas party.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.44,0:18:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was just so she could show off\Nher big Christmas tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.40,0:18:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But it was beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.61,0:18:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I remember...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.74,0:18:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.20,0:18:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna go see one after this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.41,0:18:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.83,0:18:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A Christmas tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.83,0:18:59.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.59,0:19:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.76,0:19:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Satoru Fujinuma{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.76,0:19:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're working gloves,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.64,0:19:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but it's cold up in the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.22,0:19:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't agree to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.56,0:19:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I always used to ski\Nand bobsled in this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.95,0:19:29.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I even saw red foxes once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.79,0:19:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.54,0:19:42.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.21,0:19:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I remembered the red foxes\Nrunning around at my feet.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.84,0:19:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}18 years ago, I saw it alone,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.18,0:19:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and no one believed me\Nwhen I told them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.44,0:20:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if they're a couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.94,0:20:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I bet they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.29,0:20:16.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's a lucky day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.87,0:20:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not a cloud in the sky.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.21,0:20:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.52,0:20:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A Christmas tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.98,0:20:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.27,0:20:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid? It's February.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.40,0:20:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's come back to see it in the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.99,0:20:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This Christmas tree...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.54,0:21:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?
